title: Music genres most `` liked `` on Facebook by college students
summary: The Music genres in the `` liked was Music Rock_&_Roll , who made 314540 "likes" .
The most genres Music was Jazz , with just 66380 "likes" .

In second place was Music Country with 299700 "likes" ; third place went to Music Hip_Hop with 314540 "likes" ; fourth place went to Music Classical with 66380 "likes" and fifth place went to Music Pop , who was 224140 "likes" .
gold: This statistic shows the music genres most `` liked `` by U.S. college students on Facebook as of July 2011 . Country music received 299,700 likes from U.S. college students .
